text: The AMD Ryzen 9 3900X is a 12-core CPU by Advanced Micro Devices (AMD) that runs at 3.8 GHz, which can be boosted to 4.6 GHz. It has 64 MB L3 cache. It was released on the 7th of July 2019. == References == Category:Advanced Micro Devices Category:Processors released in 2010s Category:Multi-core processors
title: AMD Ryzen 9 3900X
